### Login con username
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "john",
  "password": "password123",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### Login con email + rememberMe
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "rememberMe": true
}
